## The brief
Davies Property Development needed a professional online presence to showcase their projects and build trust with prospective buyers and investors.

## What we built
A polished, credibility-first website featuring their developments, company story, and contact details — designed to convert interest into enquiries.

## Results
- Strong first impression for prospective buyers and investors
- Improved visibility in local property-related searches
- Increased direct enquiries through the website
